item.title: Theres two ladders with the same id number one in v genreal store and zaffs shop
item.dc:creator: @The_Guardian The Guardian
item.description:
@The_Guardian wrote:

Change your case to this:

case 1747: heightLevel += 1; teleportToX = absX; teleportToY = absY; break;

That teleports their coordinates to them, but makes their height higher.
Thumbs up.
